        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 101−104. Proteromichaelia sila sp. nov. 101—Deutonymph, venter, 4 genital setae per valve; 102—Protonymph, venter, 1 genital seta per valve; 103—Larva, ventral habitus, holotrichy, genital valves absent; 104—Larva, dorsal habitus, neotrichy. 90−104 from RSA, near Potchefstroom." ;
